ed="T" n="0873a07"/><persName key="A010397">釋業方</persName>者，即<persName key="A006332">解脫<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>之法孫也。身長七尺<lb
ed="T" n="0873a08"/>五寸，古貌軒昂，垂手過膝，眉長數寸，目有<lb
ed="T" n="0873a09"/>重瞳，人望凜然。<anchor xml:id="beg0873sgsz3"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0873sgsz3"/>誦無倦，紹脫<ptr target="#n2099"/>高躅，動合<lb
ed="T" n="0873a10"/>無形，不捨利物<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2064"/>，而再修<name>梵</name>宮。時<placeName key="PL000000003794">太原府</placeName>有<lb
ed="T" n="0873a11"/>士女造立<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>像一軀，將送入<ref type="place" target="#PL000000005250">山</ref>，到<placeName key="PL000000000224">淲池<lb
ed="T" n="0873a12"/>河</placeName><ptr target="#n701"/>側，洪波汎漲。<persName key="A010397">方</persName>乃隔岸焚香啟告，河為流<lb
ed="T" n="0873a13"/>減，過<persName key="A002144">文殊</persName>畢，水還瀰溢。後終，建塔在<placeName key="PL000000005360">寺</placeName>西<lb
ed="T" n="0873a14"/>北一里，肉身見存，而多神異焉。</p>
